M|referral-program|- Budget for referral incentives?
M|referral-program|**Best for:**
M|referral-program|- Existing customers recommending to their network
M|referral-program|- Products with natural word-of-mouth
M|referral-program|- Lower-ticket or self-serve products
M|referral-program|**Characteristics:**
M|referral-program|- Referrer is an existing customer
M|referral-program|- One-time or limited rewards
M|referral-program|- Higher trust, lower volume
M|referral-program|**Best for:**
M|referral-program|- Reaching audiences you don't have access to
M|referral-program|- cnt creators, influencers, bloggers
M|referral-program|- Higher-ticket products that justify commissions
M|referral-program|**Characteristics:**
M|referral-program|- Affiliates may not be customers
M|referral-program|- Ongoing commission relationship
M|referral-program|- Higher volume, variable trust
M|referral-program|```
M|referral-program|Trigger Moment → Share Action → Convert Referred → Reward → (Loop)
M|referral-program|```
M|referral-program|**High-intent moments:**
M|referral-program|- Right after first "aha" moment
M|referral-program|- After achieving a milestone
M|referral-program|- After exceptional support
M|referral-program|- After renewing or upgrading
M|referral-program|**Ranked by effectiveness:**
M|referral-program|1. In-product sharing (highest conversion)
M|referral-program|2. Personalized link
M|referral-program|3. Email invitation
M|referral-program|4. soc sharing
M|referral-program|5. Referral code (works offline)
M|referral-program|**Single-sided rewards** (referrer only): Simpler, works for high-value products
M|referral-program|**Double-sided rewards** (both parties): Higher conversion, win-win framing
M|referral-program|**Tiered rewards**: Gamifies referral process, increases engagement
M|referral-program|**For examples and incentive sizing**: See [references/program-examples.md](references/program-examples.md)
M|referral-program|**If few customers are referring:**
M|referral-program|- Ask at better moments
M|referral-program|- Simplify sharing process
M|referral-program|- Test different incentive types
M|referral-program|- Make referral prominent in product
M|referral-program|**If referrals aren't converting:**
M|referral-program|- Improve landing experience for referred users
M|referral-program|- Strengthen incentive for new users
M|referral-program|- Ensure referrer's endorsement is visible
M|referral-program|**Incentive tests:** Amount, type, single vs. double-sided, timing
M|referral-program|**Messaging tests:** Program description, CTA copy, landing page copy
M|referral-program|**Placement tests:** Where and when the referral prompt appears
M|referral-program|| Problem | Fix |
M|referral-program||---------|-----|
M|referral-program|| Low awareness | Add prominent in-app prompts |
M|referral-program|| Low share rate | Simplify to one click |
M|referral-program|| Low conversion | Optimize referred user experience |
M|referral-program|| Fraud/abuse | Add verification, limits |
M|referral-program|| One-time referrers | Add tiered/gamified rewards |
M|referral-program|**Program health:**
M|referral-program|- Active referrers (referred someone in last 30 days)
M|referral-program|- Referral conversion rate
M|referral-program|- Rewards earned/paid
M|referral-program|**Business impact:**
M|referral-program|- % of new customers from referrals
M|referral-program|- CAC via referral vs. other channels
M|referral-program|- LTV of referred customers
M|referral-program|- Referral program ROI
M|referral-program|- Referred customers have 16-25% higher LTV
M|referral-program|- Referred customers have 18-37% lower churn
M|referral-program|- Referred customers refer others at 2-3x rate
